% Monkey Banana Problem

% Initial State:
% monkey at door
% box at window
% banana at center

% Rule: Monkey can get banana if it pushes the box,
% climbs on it, and grabs the banana.

can_get :-
    write('Monkey moves from door to window'), nl,
    write('Monkey pushes the box from window to center'), nl,
    write('Monkey climbs onto the box'), nl,
    write('Monkey grabs the banana'), nl,
    write('Monkey gets the banana successfully').

% Query:
% ?- can_get.
